# Simple confusion matrix

Plot a simple confusion matrix using matplotlib

Example:

```py
from plot_confusion_matrix import confusion_matrix
from matplotlib import pyplot

matrix = [[5, 2, 0],
		  [1, 2, 3],
		  [2, 1, 6]]

confusion_matrix(matrix)
pyplot.show(block=True)
```

